Commands

## Create .venv
```bash
python -m venv .venv
```

To active:

## Powershell
```bash
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
```

## Command Prompt
```bash
.venv\Scripts\activate.bat
```

## Update pip
```bash
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
```

## Installing FastAPI
```bash
pip install fastapi uvicorn
```